                    </div>
                    <span>This book, although not an introductory text, is widely considered the indespensable classic in writing good Prolog code. Try searching for it in the newsgroup comp.lang.prolog some time on DejaNews.<p>Prolog does a  wonderful job of hiding what is really going on. This book reveals the  wonderous truth.</span>
                  
